# Admin Dashboard Modules

Expected admin modules:
- Dashboard Overview
- Users
- Sellers
- Networks
- Inventory/Cards
- Orders
- Wallets
- Transactions
- Withdrawals
- Reports
- Audit Logs
- Notifications
- Settings
- Roles & Permissions

Expected seller modules:
- Seller Dashboard
- Networks
- Inventory
- Cards Upload
- Orders
- Wallet
- Withdrawals
- Analytics
- Settings

Every module should support where appropriate:
- create
- read
- update
- delete
- search
- filtering
- pagination
- validation
- action menus
- status management

Prefer reusable implementations.
